  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/2015_hero/public/2025-07/toponium.jpg?itok=BQX6GxzS" width="1600" height="900" alt="Artist’s impression of the short-lived union of a top quark and a top antiquark formed by the exchange of gluons" />





